<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA69">
<l>muṭimēṟ koṭumatiyāṉ mukkaṇā ṉalla</l>
<l>vaṭimēṟ koṭumatiyōṅ kūṟṟaip - paṭimēṟ</l>
<l>kuṉiyavala māmaṭimai koṇṭāṭap peṟṟō</l>
<l>miṉiyavala muṇṭō vemakku</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>We who, at the feet of him with three eyes, him with the curved moon</l>
<l>on [his] crown do not think well of cruel Death, we who have obtained</l>
<l>to cherish servantship that is the strength to bend down on earth,</l>
<l>will there now be [any] affliction for us?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
